text: Hashan Dumindu (born 4 July 1995) is a Sri Lankan first-class cricketer. He was part of Sri Lanka's squad for the 2014 ICC Under-19 Cricket World Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Sri Lankan cricketers Category:People from Western Province, Sri Lanka Category:Galle Guardians cricketers Category:Kegalle District cricketers
